description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;East Suffolk and North Essex NHS Foundation Trust (ESNEFT) are excited to be able to offer a Full Time post for a Materials Management Officer. You will be based in the Procurement Materials Management department at Colchester General Hospital. &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;It is an exciting time for the Trust following our recent merge to create the largest NHS organisation in the region. Our scale will provide you with great opportunities to develop skills and experience. With the implementation of the new structure and national developments this is an exciting time to be part of Procurement. ESNEFT Procurement is a progressive department, looking to integrate with clinical and operational colleagues, define innovative ways of working and delivering on financial targets. As part of the new Trust the Procurement department has restructured and is looking to further supplement the skills and expertise in place and if your aspiration matches ours we’d welcome your application.&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
